Sentencas: In this study, novel SrCe1 - xYbxO3 (-) (alpha)(x = 0, 0.05, 0.10, 0.15)-(Na/K)Cl composite electrolytes were synthesized at low temperature (750 degrees C).
Titulo: Novel SrCe1- xYbxO3 - α-(Na/K)Cl composite electrolytes for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The structural and microstructural properties of the composite electrolytes are observed by X-ray diffraction (XRD) and scanning electron microscopy (SEM).
Titulo: Novel SrCe1- xYbxO3 - α-(Na/K)Cl composite electrolytes for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: It was found that the upper doping limit of Yb3+ in SrCeO3 is 15 mol%.
Titulo: Novel SrCe1- xYbxO3 - α-(Na/K)Cl composite electrolytes for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The XRD results shown that no chemical reactions take place between SrCe1 - xYbxO3 (-) (alpha) (x = 0, 0.05, 0.10, 0.15) and NaCl/KCl.
Titulo: Novel SrCe1- xYbxO3 - α-(Na/K)Cl composite electrolytes for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The SEM images revealed that NaCl/KCl is coated on the surface of SrCe1 - xYbxO3 (-) (alpha) (x = 0, 0.05, 0.10, 0.15) act as a binder.
Titulo: Novel SrCe1- xYbxO3 - α-(Na/K)Cl composite electrolytes for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The electrical conductivity is determined by impedance spectroscopy.
Titulo: Novel SrCe1- xYbxO3 - α-(Na/K)Cl composite electrolytes for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The log sigma similar to log (pO(2)) plots results indicate that the composites are almost pure ionic conductors.
Titulo: Novel SrCe1- xYbxO3 - α-(Na/K)Cl composite electrolytes for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: Finally, the excellent performance of SCYb15-NK is obtained with a maximum power density of 615 mW.cm(-2) at 700 degrees C.
Titulo: Novel SrCe1- xYbxO3 - α-(Na/K)Cl composite electrolytes for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells
